channel.title: Not Named Yet _ 508 Project
channel.description:
[b]IMPORTANT: SUGGEST SOME NAMES IF YOU HAVE IDEAS! :)[/b]
You might have seen my "Clean508" base in the downloads section, this is what I'm basing it off of. Note, I'll still be releasing Clean508 Full Version (1.0), just after I re-write some important things.
[b]Base: BerkyScape 508 (Bulby)[/b]
[b]Aim: To create a fun, noob-friendly 508 deob server, with stability first and content second.[/b] [b]Realistic or "Original": Realistic, like RuneScape.[/b] [b]Age Group: 15+[/b] (At least hopefully, hoping to have a good community, players I can rely on, etc...[/b]
No pictures right now, but I can near promise you that I will have pictures in the [b]following 24 hours.[/b] (So please no WBMs)
[size=15pt][b][font=Green]What I plan to do:[/font][/b][/size] (More stability wise)
Rewrite combat Improve stability Make a better, hacker-free client.
[size=15pt][b][font=Green]What I plan to do:[/font][/b][/size] (More features wise)
Create Herblore Create Thieving Create Mining Create Woodcutting Create very basic, low level things to do (Adding cows in their correct places, drops, all that stuff)
Elite content (High-leveled) will come in later. Right now all I want to finish is what I have above this sentence.
~Albert
P.S. Again, pictures will be posted in the following 24 hrs.
